Product Version     25.10    Cadence Design Systems, Inc.
timing_context...id_module_list(25.10)  timing_context...id_module_list(25.10)

Name
       timing_context_continue_on_invalid_module_list

Syntax
       timing_context_continue_on_invalid_module_list {true | false}

       Default: false

       Enables to continue timing analysis without generating timing context.

       When set to true, the software will continue with timing analysis with-
       out generating timing context, when all the specified modules/instances
       are invalid.

       To set this global variable, use the set command.

